UNITED STATES of America, Appellant, v. Reese E. DAVIS, Appellee. No. 6513. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Feb. 10, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Ordered appeal dismissed in above cause pursuant to stipulation of counsel for the respective parties; mandate forthwith.
